query:
SELECT cs.id, cs.uniqueId, cs.baseTemplateId, cs.organizationId, cs.version, o.customerNumber
FROM customSuperprompts cs
LEFT JOIN organizations o ON cs.organizationId = o.id
LIMIT 10;
